prop.text: Brassawiking is so powerful, he finished this maze in record time!
I've been running the maze for hours now. Might take a pause to swim a bit.
Hmm. I wonder if there are more secrets like this one...?
Pst! There are secret paths in some places. Dont just follow the roads!
There is a rumor that a land full of desserts are on the other side.
The people ahead will explain the rules!
Did you get the rules? Good! Now go ahead and dont get lost!
Hello! Welcome to the Maze!
The third rule of the maze is "Stay off the mountains and rocks. No climbing!"
The second rule of the maze is "Keep gravity on until you finish the maze"
The first rule of the maze is "you dont talk about the maze".
Are you lost? HAHA! ......me too.
"The truth"
Hmm..  looks like another dead end.
The truth is out there...
Remember to stay hydrated! There's some potable water here.
Wait...   which way did I come from...?
This is my meditation corner. Isn't it super chill?
Good work with the labyrinth! Now stock up for the desert.
Hmm. I might stay here a while before I leave for the desert.
Those who seek has yet to find, keep your peace and keep your mind.
"You are a- a- a- a-MAZEing" - the great prophet Saucedo
Wow! You made it! Your prize is the great wisdom written on this here tablet...
Ahead is the great dessert desert. Hope you're ready for it!
I feel scammed. They told me of great treassure in the maze, and those words of wisdom...? That's it?!
